                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1525-18440506 t18440506-1525-punishment-146"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Edward Bullock, Esq.</hi>
